Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{What the hell are you doing?}Cô đang làm cái quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{What's all this about?}Chuyện này là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{ kinds of guys?}{\i0}Gã đó thích kiểu này à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.92,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What are you saying?}Anh đang nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.88,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Gren... isn't like that.}Gren không phải như thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{Gren?}Gren ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{"Mangan", with "ura-dora"...}"Mangan" và "ura-dora".
