Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you catch him, I'll let you back on.}{\i0}Bắt được hắn thì cậu có thể quay lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:15.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hello?}A lô?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm overhead.}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi ở phía trên anh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{building closest to the sky.}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi sẽ gặp anh trên nóc tòa nhà cao nhất.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'll send a woman over.}{\i1}Một phụ nữ sẽ giao nó.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I don't care.}{\i0}{\i1}Không sao.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{liked to see you as well.}{\i0}{\i1}Nhưng tôi muốn gặp anh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:39.04,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{You broke the Bebop, but kept\Nthe Swordfish and Hammerhead mobile.}Cô phá hỏng Bebop\Nnhưng lại để yên cho Cá Kiếm và Đầu Búa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{Did you leave that message\Nso that we'd come find you?}{\i1}Đó là cách cô nói, "Đi tìm tôi" à?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:44.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{You've got to be kidding.}{\i1}Đừng ngớ ngẩn thế.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Were you just testing us?}Cô đang thử chúng tôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{Why did you come here?}Sao anh lại đến?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{I want my money back. [13 frame link]}Tôi muốn lấy lại tiền.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{The safe...}Tiền trong két sắt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{only had 20,000 in it.}Trong đó chỉ có 20.000.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{Is that so?}Có nhiêu đó thôi ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dummy.}Vui ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.11,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hey...}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.17,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Who is Julia?}Julia là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:07.37,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{Dunno... but she has\Nsomething to do with Spike.}Không biết.\NNhưng cô ấy có liên quan gì đó đến Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's all I know.}Tôi chỉ biết thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{Souvenir, souvenir, is it here yet?}Quà ở đâu? Nó có ở đây không? Nó đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{It has an EX+ ranking. It's real.}Nó được xếp hạng EX+. Là hàng thật đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hand it over.}Giao qua đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is the Titan Opal that you requested.}Đây là viên đá quý Titan cô yêu cầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{Give Gren my regards.}Cho gửi lời hỏi thăm Gren.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{You saved me from that scorpion back then.}Hồi đó anh đã cứu tôi khỏi con bọ cạp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yet you sold me out.}Vậy mà lại bán đứng tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{Gren?}Gren?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:05.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{Long time no see.}Lâu rồi không gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:07.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{What are you up to?}Anh làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{You gave me that music box because you}Anh đưa tôi hộp nhạc đó,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{never thought I'd take\Nit apart and examine it?}nghĩ rằng\Ntôi sẽ không bao giờ mở ra kiểm tra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{You found the transmitter.}Tìm ra hệ thống điều khiển rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:18.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{Julia was the one who found it.}Là Julia tìm ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:22.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{She realized as soon as she\Nheard it was a gift from you.}Cô ấy biết\Nngay khi nghe nói đó là quà của anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{And what about it? [9 frames]}Rồi thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{Are you trying to kill me again?}Anh lại định giết tôi lần nữa à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{We fought in the war together...}Ta từng là đồng đội.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{We were comrades...}Từng chiến đấu bên nhau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{We fought together...\Non that desert battlefield...}Ta đã cùng chiến đấu\Ntrên chiến trường sa mạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{I looked up to you...}Tôi đã rất ngưỡng mộ anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{I believed in you...}Tôi tin tưởng ở anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{There is nothing there to believe.}Chả có gì để tin cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nor is there a need to believe.}Cũng không cần phải tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{Sir Vicious!}Anh Vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{In this world, there is nothing to believe in.}Niềm tin trong thế giới này ư...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{Vicious!}Vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Lin's soul won't be saved since he lost\Nhis life protecting someone like you!}Nếu Lin phải chết vì cứu người như anh,\Ncậu ấy sẽ không được siêu thoát!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm not what he was protecting!}Cậu ấy không bảo vệ tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{He protected the rules! [9 frames]}{\i1}Cậu ấy bảo vệ Hội Đồng!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're in the way!}Anh cản đường tôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Come on, get a grip! Hey!}Này! Gắng lên! Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{Where is Julia? Where did she go?!}Julia đâu? Cô ấy đi đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{Do you know her?}Anh biết cô ấy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{Where is she now?}Giờ cô ấy ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{He hit some vital organs.}Anh đã bị nội thương.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:10.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shit, would an ambulance\Ncome to a place like this?}Chết tiệt, xe cứu thương\Ncó đến nơi khỉ ho cò gáy này không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,{Can you lift me up into the pod again?}Anh đưa tôi vào buồng lái được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{I want to go to Titan...}Tôi muốn đến Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.65,Main,split,0,0,0,,{You can't possibly last in your condition!}Anh sẽ không sống sót trong tình trạng đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.10,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It would take too long!}Lâu lắm mới tới!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{I won't last long anyway...}Đằng nào tôi cũng chẳng sống lâu được.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:32.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dying during the voyage\Nwould be a good way to go...}Chết khi đang viễn du\Ncũng không phải cái chết quá tệ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:37.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{I want to return there... one more time.}Tôi muốn quay lại nơi đó một lần nữa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{I want to be as close as I can...}hoặc đến gần nơi đó nhất có thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{Please...}Làm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{I see.}Tôi biết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{You are Spike.}Anh là Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{Julia was always talking about you...}Julia nhắc về anh suốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{That your two eyes were\Nof different colors...}"Đôi mắt anh ấy có hai màu".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's what she said...}Cô ấy đã nói thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:15.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{That you get a strange feeling\Nwhen you look into his eyes...}Và cô ấy nói khi nhìn vào mắt anh\Nsẽ có cảm giác rất lạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{What was she doing?}Cô ấy đã làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{In the corner seat of the bar...}Ngồi ở góc của quán bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:26.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{She always sat there while\NI wasn't paying attention...}Cô ấy đã luôn ngồi ở đó\Ntừ trước khi tôi để ý đến cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:31.17,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{She always requested the same song...}Cô ấy luôn yêu cầu cùng một bài hát...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{and smiled.}và mỉm cười.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:36.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{Sadly...}Cô ấy cười...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{smiled.}nụ cười rất buồn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{What do you have?}Được gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:50.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nothing.}{\i0}{\i1}Không.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hurry up and get in. We're taking off.}{\i0}{\i1}Nhanh quay trở lại đi. Ta sắp cất cánh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:06.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{Julia...}Julia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{What? [9 frames]}Sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Mm... nothing. Just an adult's idle muttering.}Không có gì cả. Tự nói chuyện thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{Where did all of you guys go?}Mọi người đã đi đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{Someplace good.}Một nơi dễ chịu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ed's the only one left out!}Bỏ mặc Ed một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:20.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'll tell you someday.}Hôm nào đó kể cho nghe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nah, it's okay, really.}Không, không quan tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:26.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're not being cute.}Không dễ thương chút nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{The star fell, Bull.}Một ngôi sao băng kìa, Bò Mộng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.81,0:21:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{That is no ordinary star.}Đó không phải ngôi sao bình thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:50.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{That is the tear of a warrior.}Đó là nước mắt của một chiến binh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,{What is a warrior?}Một chiến binh là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.88,0:21:56.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{One who has finished his battle\Nsomewhere on this planet...}Một người phải chiến đấu\Nở đâu đó trên hành tinh này,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.19,0:22:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{A pitiful soul that could not\Nbelieve in the Great Spirit...}một linh hồn đáng thương\Nkhông tin vào Thần Linh Vĩ Đại.
